b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":584,"category_name":"Events","pr_category_id":"4","title_name":"Astral Raids Are Coming Soon!","message":"<div>Astral Raids will arrive in Event Quests starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1563602400\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/011f0d1be28deb9ad8be621a29e7529a.png\\"><\/div><div>The Astral.<\/div><div>It is the culmination of countless memories amassed from the corners of the world.<\/div><div>It is the recollection of past ruin on the constant brink of reemergence.<\/div><div>It is the calamities that descended the world in bygone days.<\/div><div>It is a call to cleanse a world scourged by the flames of catastrophe!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>See below for more information on Astral Raids.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/7d6536f753d908646d15bd0f63d50d83.png\\"><\/div><div>\\u25a0Featured Boss<\/div><div>Hypnos<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Astral Raids Overview<\/div><div>\\u30fbAstral Raids are event quests where you can fight against past raid bosses, but they are only available on the weekends.<\/div><div>\\u30fbTo challenge Astral Raids quests, you will need to use Astral Pieces.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Astral Pieces<\/div><div>\\u30fbAstral Pieces can be obtained by clearing main campaign quests and event quests.<\/div><div>\\u30fbYou will not receive Astral Pieces for clearing The Mercurial Gauntlet quests.<\/div><div>\\u30fbYou will not receive Astral Pieces for clearing quests while astral raids are active.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe maximum number of Astral Pieces you can hold is 300.<\/div><div>\\u30fbIf you obtain Astral Pieces after reaching the limit, those Astral Pieces will be lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Treasure Trade<\/div><div>An Astral Raids section will be added to the Treasure Trade <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1563602400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div>Also, the order in which the various Treasure Trades are displayed will be changed around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1563170400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 \/ 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in Astral Raids.<\/div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 \/ 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1563170400,"prev_article_id":"590","next_article_id":"585","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/011f0d1be28deb9ad8be621a29e7529a.png","update_time":1569487937}}}'